    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Relative hemolysis index predictions satisfy RH < 1 at all five operating points. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed at MRL 2. Note: aleatory uncertainty in the global hemolysis index validation result was characterized qualitatively by reviewer judgment rather than through a structured UQ framework; this is considered acceptable given the supporting quantitative UQ on velocity and pressure validation results and the medium model influence classification.",
